column5: Yup, stuck at work on opening morning....  Here's my "new to me" boat that I can't wait to get wet.
Looks great, congrats! I hope you're having a better day.
Aside from the fact that I am working instead of fishing....my day has been going better.  Still havent found my wallet though...
Nice Boat I hope you get out and enjoy it soon.  I used to have a similar set up an 18ft Lund SSV with a 50hp Honda.  Tough old boat I tell ya!Looking forward to the fishing reports!!!!!!!
sweet ride enjoy the eyes when you get out
I think the wallet is history.  I've lost two in my day.  Pain in the butt to get all the cards and ID back.  On the up side very nice boat.  Now just get out there and fish already...lol
